      • setStarted

        public void setStarted()
        Start a line, this adds the line to the startedLines HashMap and startedFinishLines if this line is a finish line. If this is the only line started now, it also starts the listener for player movement.

      • setStopped

        public void setStopped()
        Stops this line and removes it from startedLines HashMap and startedFinishLines HashMap. If there are no started finish lines left, stop the listener for player movement.
